Framework (Spring, Hibernate, Junit)

pre-defined structure or platform that reusable, - components, libraries, set rules regulations

time saves, reduces boilerplate code, improves maintainability and scalability, has built in security


Collections  - Framework
-----------
Pre-defined classes and interface

java.util -> package


Inerface : List, Set, Map

List - ArrayList, LinkedList           - Odered Collection, duplicates
Set - HashSet, TreeSet, LinkedHashSet  - Collection unique
Map - HashMap, TreeMap, LinkedHashMap  - Key - value pair key is unique, value is duplicate
